name: Cute Elements - Elementals and physics
description:
Water wants to play with her elemental friends, but when she arrives she finds them caged, you must help her to free her friends who also have incredible powers and together complete the game, it's a fun puzzle, a creative game, will you be able to do it?

Fun physics puzzles where each adorable character controls an element of nature, water, fire, wind, metal and more elements.

Momentos divertidos durante el desarrollo XD (gameplays)
